547
00:30:50,751 --> 00:30:51,392
(can be you.)

548
00:30:54,551 --> 00:30:55,232
Qing Gang.

549
00:30:56,912 --> 00:30:57,992
You're silly.

550
00:31:00,992 --> 00:31:03,152
Would you still give me this

551
00:31:04,712 --> 00:31:05,712
