570
00:31:52,152 --> 00:31:53,831
She has done justice to her heroic name
as Jiang Bead Flying Flame.

571
00:31:54,351 --> 00:31:55,751
She dedicated herself to the nation
despite her gender.

572
00:31:56,912 --> 00:31:57,311
Xuelu.

